title: Classy Updates w/ Modern Features-1 bed/1-bath in Treelined Area
posting_body: ['We have a beautifully updated 1-bedroom apartment in a tree-lined neighborhood and gated apartment community.', 'Enjoy all the fresh new amenities and, granite kitchen countertop, easy-to-maintain solid flooring, modern light fixtures and more!', 'AMENITIES:', '- Laundry Hookups', '- Easy-to-Maintain Vinyl Plank Flooring', '- Air Conditioning', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Garbage Disposal', '- New Appliances', '- Shower/Tub Combo', '- Dual Paned Windows', "In addition to all the new features, you'll also get the benefit of paying rent throughout the month (instead of just the 1st!) through a 3rd party app called Flex.", '(Terms apply, please ask our leasing manager for more info!)', 'Please review our rental qualifications then call us to schedule a tour.', 'show contact info', 'Dial ext 2 to bypass the long message.', 'You can also email us at bayarea@ redwood - property.', 'com.', 'Thank you!', 'We look forward to meeting you.', 'Rental Qualifications:', '- Credit Score =', '600+', '- Income = 2.5x Rent', '- No Prior Evictions', "Total move-in costs = first month's rent + security deposit (SD = 1-1.5x Rent)", '*Sorry, no pets.', 'We look forward to hearing from you.', 'Thank you!']
